message.text:
JOIN ADVOCAMP🥰

Joining the Advocacy & Campaigns Department means being at the frontline of conversations that matter. Back when I was part of the Executive Committee last year, I had the chance to speak up on key issues mula sa NO to MROTC, HIV/AIDS Awareness, hanggang EDSA People Power Revolution.

I also got to craft statements na tumutulong sa mga estudyante na maging informed sa kung ano ang nangyayari sa bansa natin dahil naniniwala ako na hindi pwedeng manahimik kapag may kailangang ipaglaban.

If you’re ready to turn your passion into action, this is your sign. Sama-sama tayong gumawa ng campaigns na hindi lang maingay online, pero may tunay na impact sa komunidad.

message.text:
JOIN ADVOCAMP🥰

Joining the Advocacy & Campaigns Department means being at the frontline of conversations that matter. Back when I was part of the Executive Committee last year, I had the chance to speak up on key issues mula sa NO to MROTC, HIV/AIDS Awareness, hanggang EDSA People Power Revolution.

I also got to craft statements na tumutulong sa mga estudyante na maging informed sa kung ano ang nangyayari sa bansa natin dahil naniniwala ako na hindi pwedeng manahimik kapag may kailangang ipaglaban.

If you’re ready to turn your passion into action, this is your sign. Sama-sama tayong gumawa ng campaigns na hindi lang maingay online, pero may tunay na impact sa komunidad.

message.text:
JOIN ADVOCAMP🥰

Joining the Advocacy & Campaigns Department means being at the frontline of conversations that matter. Back when I was part of the Executive Committee last year, I had the chance to speak up on key issues mula sa NO to MROTC, HIV/AIDS Awareness, hanggang EDSA People Power Revolution.

I also got to craft statements na tumutulong sa mga estudyante na maging informed sa kung ano ang nangyayari sa bansa natin dahil naniniwala ako na hindi pwedeng manahimik kapag may kailangang ipaglaban.

If you’re ready to turn your passion into action, this is your sign. Sama-sama tayong gumawa ng campaigns na hindi lang maingay online, pero may tunay na impact sa komunidad.

Calling Tamaraws from every institute! 🔰

We are 3rd year BA Communication students under Convergent Media track, currently conducting a survey for our Communication Planning course.

We’re looking for students of any year level, 1st year to 5th year, to answer our forms regarding FEU's Guidance and Counseling Services.

Your response will be a huge help to us! Thank you so much in advance! 💗

cc: Nashly Fae Mondejar Louela Luna Chesca Regala 

LINK:
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfliSYGFHoCVlxGy3hE-bNYa_nAmFESJfjCfw7Wwc7BxkglIg/viewform
